Example dataset from Rosenbaum, Mama, & Algom (2017)

stroop_df.Rd

some sample reaction time data from a 2x2 Stroop experiment

stroop_df

Format

A data frame with 200 rows and 4 variables:

subject

factor subject ids

congruency

factor congruency codes, Congruent vs. Incongruent

posture

factor whether the participant was sitting or standing

rts

numeric reaction time

Details

Example dataset from Rosenbaum, Mama, & Algom (2017) downloaded from OSF, and loaded into R in long-format. See pre-processing script in data-raw.
